{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Ayesha! The day has finally come when you can be of use to me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's wrong, Bell? What do you mean by \"be of use\"...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You can only answer in two ways:<CR>\"It'll be my pleasure!\" or<CR>\"Yaaay, I'm so happy!\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "(Whaaat...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, just listen to what I have to say. Oh, before that, I have a question."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "How long ago was it when you first started synthesizing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Umm, about 10 years. I first started when my grandpa was teaching me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Okay, so you've been doing it for a while. What kind of things did you do to train?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Like, memorizing the names and shapes of all medicinal herbs, synthesizing the same things over and over...that stuff."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, that's so tedious!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, but it's fun. I could be grinding herbs in a mortar all day long, and I still wouldn't get bored."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, that I don't think I'd agree...<CR>My mind would go completely blank."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but I think I got the gist of it. So, here comes the main point of this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "To tell you the truth, I'm still doing my apprenticeship."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, well, I'd assume so at your age."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, age doesn't really have anything to do with it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I basically consider myself to be a<CR>full-fledged witch, but my<CR>great-great-grandmother doesn't<CR>acknowledge it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I see... Training to be a witch...<CR>What would that be like?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Casting the same spell over and over<CR>again, facing the wall, or flying a<CR>long distance with heavy luggage?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's with your tedious imagination? I don't do that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "We're not like that. We get to choose our tasks, so we're free to do anything we want!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Whoa. Then I'd be totally lost about what I should actually do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That's it! I've done various things up till now, but Great-great-grandmother won't approve any of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I've kinda reached a deadlock, and I thought of getting you to help me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Help...? Hmm, I wonder if there's anything I'd be able to do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Easy-peasy, just make the thing that's written here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Umm...\"Madder Holy Iron\"?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "This book is really difficult. I don't think I can make it right away, Bell..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Well, maybe not. This is a magic book..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I'll try, because studying it might do me good, but can I have some time?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Of course. If you need clarifications for anything, come ask me. I can help."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x19a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm counting on you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, it's a bit difficult for me right now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "But if I can understand this book,<CR>I might be able to synthesize more<CR>powerful things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Alright, I'll give it a try."
        }
    ]
}